<HL>
   Dividend News:
   Philadelphia
   Electric Reduces
   Dividend by 45%
   ----
   By Beatrice E. Garcia
   Staff Reporter of The Wall Street Journal
</HL>
<DATE>
04/24/90
</DATE>
<SO>
WALL STREET JOURNAL (J), PAGE C22
</SO>
